high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the pan from the counter.
Walk over to face the fridge.
Open the fridge door, put the pan inside of the fridge, close the door, open the door, take the pan out, close the door.
Walk over to the sink on the right.
Put the pan down on the counter to the left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: To chill a pan and put it on the counter next to the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and go straight, then turn left at the counter with the pot on it.
Pick up the pot from the counter.
Turn right and go forward to the end of the counter, turn right and go forward, then turn left of the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the pot inside, chill it, then take it out.
Turn left and go forward, then turn right to face the sink.
Put the pot on the counter to the left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold pot on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and walk left to the counter to the left of the stove.
Grab the pot from the counter.
Turn right and walk and turn right again and walk to the fridge on the left.
Chill the pot for 2 seconds in the fridge.
Turn left and walk to the sink.
Place the pot to the left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled pot to the left of the sink.
